GoogleCloudDiscoveryengineV1alphaDocumen.description: AclRestriction to model complex inheritance restrictions. Example: Modeling a "Both Permit" inheritance, where to access a child document, user needs to have access to parent document. Document Hierarchy - Space_S --> Page_P. Readers: Space_S: group_1, user_1 Page_P: group_2, group_3, user_2 Space_S ACL Restriction - { "acl_info": { "readers": [ { "principals": [ { "group_id": "group_1" }, { "user_id": "user_1" } ] } ] } } Page_P ACL Restriction. { "acl_info": { "readers": [ { "principals": [ { "group_id": "group_2" }, { "group_id": "group_3" }, { "user_id": "user_2" } ], }, { "principals": [ { "group_id": "group_1" }, { "user_id": "user_1" } ], } ] } }
